  "is_vocab": false,
  "stimulus_html": "<p>The antipsychotic drug flupentixol is prepared by the following scheme:</p>\n<img class=\"scaled-down\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBdjRUIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--393fd1f5da7a84ded05d9ea74a924030f566e427/OChem_11_EC_049.jpg\" alt=\"Compound A undergoes a multi-step reaction to produce Flupentixol through the formation of intermediate compounds B, C, D, and E.\">",
  "questions": [
    {
      "id": 355458,
      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "What alkyl chloride <b>B</b> reacts with amine <b>A</b> to form <b>C</b>?",
      "answers": [],
      "hints": [],
      "formats": [
        "free-response"
      ],
      "combo_choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": 355459,
      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "Compound <b>C</b> is treated with SOCl<sub>2</sub>, and the product is allowed to react with magnesium metal to give a Grignard reagent <b>D</b>. What is the structure of <b>D</b>?",
      "answers": [],
      "hints": [],
      "formats": [
        "free-response"
      ],
      "combo_choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": 355460,
      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "We’ll see in Section 19.7 that Grignard reagents add to ketones, such as <b>E</b>, to give tertiary alcohols, such as <b>F</b>. Because of the newly formed chirality center, compound <b>F</b> exists as a pair of enantiomers. Draw both, and assign <i>R,S</i> configurations.",
      "answers": [],
      "hints": [],
      "formats": [
        "free-response"
      ],
      "combo_choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": 355461,
      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "Two stereoisomers of flupentixol are subsequently formed from <b>F</b>, but only one is shown. Draw the other isomer, and identify the type of stereoisomerism.",
      "answers": [],
      "hints": [],
      "formats": [
        "free-response"
      ],
      "combo_choices": []
    }
